quran[5{c,v,t}:
5,104,aur jab un se kaha jata hai ke aao uss qanoon ki taraf jo Allah ne nazil kya hai aur aaoPeghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallamki taraf to woh jawab dete hain ke hamaray liye to bas wohi tareeqa kaafi hai jis par hum ne apne baap dada ko paaya hai kya yeh baap dada hi ki taqleed kiye chalay jayen ge khuwa woh kuch nah jantay hon aur sahih rasta ki inhen khabar hi nah ho ?
5,105,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, apni fikar karo, kisi dosray ki gumraahi se tumhara kuch nahi bigartaa agar tum khud raah raast par ho, Allah ki taraf tum sab ko palat kar jana hai, phir woh tumhe bta day ga ke tum kya karte rahay ho"
5,106,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jab tum mein se kisi ki mout ka waqt aa jaye aur woh wasiyat kar raha ho to is ke liye shahadat ka nisaab yeh hai ke tumhari jamaat mein se do sahib Adal aadmi gawah banaye jayen, ya agar tum safar ki haalat mein ho aur wahan mout ki museebat paish aa jaye to ghair mslmon hi mein se do gawah le liye ja-ayn phir agar koi shak par jaye to namaz ke baad dono gawahoon ko ( masjid mein ) rok liya jaye aur woh khuda ki qasam kha kar kahin ke"" hum kisi zaati faiday ke aiwz shahadat baichnay walay nahi hain, aur khuwa koi hamara rishta daar hi kyun nah ho ( hum is ki riayat karne walay nahi ) aur nah khuda wastay ki gawahi ko hum chupaney walay hain, agar hum ne ysa kya to gunah gaaron mein shumaar hon ge """
5,107,"lekin agar pata chal jaye ke un dono ne apne aap ko gunah mein mubtala kya hai to phir un ki jagah do aur shakhs jo un ki bah nisbat shahadat dainay ke liye ahal tar hon un logon mein se kharray hon jin ki haq talfi hui ho, aur woh khuda ki qasam kha kar kahin ke"" hamari shahadat unn ki shahadat se ziyada Bar haq hai aur hum ne apne gawahi mein koi zayad-ti nahi ki hai, agar hum aisa karen to zaalmon mein se hon ge """
5,108,"is tareeqa se ziyada tawaqqa ki ja sakti hai ke log theek theek shahadat den ge, ya kam az kam is baat hi ka khauf karen ge ke un ki qasmon ke baad dosri qasmon se kahin un ki tardeed nah ho jaye Allah se daro aur suno, Allah nafarmani karne walon ko apni rahnumai se mahroom kar deta hai"
